%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20things%20Tesla%20needs%20to%20do%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224501%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20vehicle%20under%20Tesla%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed9020b8b41a9673fc7645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20faces%20an%20uphill%20struggle%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20grow%20its%20car%20business%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EPATRICK%20PLEUL%2FPOOL%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-history-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%3C%2Fa%3E%20first-quarter%20delivery%20report%20showed%20the%20EV%20giant's%20business%20is%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndustry%20observers%20told%20BI%20what%20Tesla%20has%20to%20do%20to%20stay%20competitive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20more%20models%2C%20advanced%20tech%2C%20and%20advertising%20could%20be%20the%20answer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20just%20can't%20seem%20to%20catch%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20has%20fallen%20amid%20a%20backlash%20against%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20its%20latest%20delivery%20report%20on%20Wednesday%20showed%20its%20car%20sales%20business%20is%20fundamentally%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20Q1%20deliveries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-delivery-numbers-numbers-first-quarter-elon-musk-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edropped%2013%25%20from%20the%20previous%20year%20to%20just%20336%2C700%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20well%20short%20of%20analysts'%20forecasts.%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20who%20is%20typically%20bullish%20on%20the%20automaker%2C%20called%20the%20figures%20%26quot%3Ba%20disaster%26quot%3B%20that%20showed%20the%20automaker%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-blown%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20some%20of%20the%20auto%20industry's%20keenest%20observers%20about%20what%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20do%20to%20turn%20things%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bcc8ef10-1c1e-49c9-81eb-e34fc6e3fe71%5C%22%3ELaunch%20more%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20political%20backlash%20against%20Musk%20has%20grabbed%20headlines%2C%20lead%20editor%20for%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20Sean%20Tucker%20told%20BI%20that%20Tesla's%20aging%20product%20lineup%20was%20a%20big%20reason%20deliveries%20were%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20carmaker%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20a%20downward%20trend%20in%20delivery%20numbers%20since%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20grew%20from%202020%20to%202023%2C%20and%20then%20they%20started%20shrinking%2C%26quot%3B%20Tucker%20said%2C%20citing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Fcar-news%2Famerica-hit-peak-tesla-in-february-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20found%20Tesla%20hit%20a%20peak%20of%2060%2C325%20monthly%20US%20sales%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Cybertruck%20with%20Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6630f1de10dfcda40964c3f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Cybertruck%20has%20failed%20to%20drive%20sales%20since%20it%20launched%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EFrederic%20J.%20Brown%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20automaker%20began%20selling%20a%20revamped%20version%20of%20its%20bestselling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-y-new-design-could-make-car-buyers-upgrade-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModel%20Y%20earlier%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20has%20not%20launched%20a%20new%20vehicle%20since%20the%20Cybertruck%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FQ4-2024-Kelley-Blue-Book-EV-Sales-Report-revised.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECybertruck%20was%20the%20top-selling%20vehicle%20in%20the%20small%20EV%20truck%20market%20in%202024%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20pickup%20has%20failed%20to%20boost%20Tesla's%20sales%20numbers.%20In%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025%2C%20the%20company%20sold%20just%2012%2C991%20%26quot%3Bother%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20includes%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-truck-cybertruck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECybertruck%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Model%20S%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-x-suv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModel%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Lenox%2C%20business%20professor%20and%20EV%20industry%20expert%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia's%20Darden%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20European%20and%20Chinese%20manufacturers%20now%20have%20EV%20models%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Beating%20into%26quot%3B%20the%20lead%20Tesla%20once%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20just%20seen%20massive%20entry%20by%20all%20the%20global%20existing%20incumbent%20auto%20manufacturers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Valdez%20Streaty%2C%20director%20of%20industry%20insights%20at%20Cox%20Automotive%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20number%20of%20EVs%20on%20the%20US%20market%20had%20ballooned%20from%20around%2019%20in%202020%20to%2078.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20this%20has%20made%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-more-affordable-what-we-know-model-y-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunch