ker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d51992e-5fec-47ec-91dd-c4305ae18a2e%5C%22%3ERelease%20more%20advanced%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELenox%20said%20Tesla%20also%20needed%20to%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bpushing%20the%20technology%20forward%20so%20they%20can%20get%20more%20capacity%20and%20lower%20cost%20out%20of%20the%20battery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELenox%20told%20BI%20that%20Tesla's%20Chinese%20competitor%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-chinese-automaker-byd-rose-to-challenge-tesla-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBYD%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0not%20only%20has%20more%20models%20on%20the%20road%20but%20also%20dominates%20the%20battery%20value%20chain.%20BYD%20reported%20416%2C00%20deliveries%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20Tuesday%2C%20far%20more%20than%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FtAR3I%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22BYD%20pulls%20ahead%20of%20Tesla%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22474%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBYD's%20latest%20advancement%20in%20charging%20strengthens%20its%20position%20as%20a%20leading%20global%20EV%20company%2C%20Lenox%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBYD%20recently%20announced%20new%20chargers%20that%20it%20said%20could%20add%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-unveils-fast-chargers-400km-range-5-minutes-tesla-challenge-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E250%20miles%20of%20range%20to%20an%20EV%20in%20five%20minutes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%201%2C000%20kW%20chargers%20are%20four%20times%20as%20powerful%20as%20Tesla's%20current%20250%20kW%20chargers%2C%20which%20Tesla%20has%20said%20can%20add%20200%20miles%20of%20range%20in%2015%20minutes.%20Tesla%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20500%20kW%20chargers%20this%20year%2C%20but%20that's%