com%2Fworld-leaders-react-to-trumps-liberation-day-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%2C%20analysts%20at%20investment%20bank%20Citi%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20Apple%20cannot%20get%20exempted%20this%20time%20and%20assuming%20Apple%20gets%20hit%20by%20the%20accumulative%2054%25%20China%20tariffs%20and%20does%20not%20pass%20it%20through%2C%20we%20estimate%20about%209%25%20negative%20impact%20to%20the%20company's%20total%20gross%20margin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20Jefferies%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20Thursday%20note%20that%20in%20their%20worst-case%20scenario%20%E2%80%94%20one%20in%20which%20the%2027%20million%20iPhones%20made%20in%20China%20and%20imported%20to%20the%20US%20are%20subject%20to%20the%2054%25%20tariff%20%E2%80%94%20Apple's%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20could%20be%20reduced%20by%2014%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20paints%20a%20less-than-pretty%20picture%20for%20Apple%20and%2C%20potentially%2C%20its%20consumers.%20Without%20an%20exemption%2C%20there%20could%20be%20more%20expensive%20iPhones%20on%20the%20way%2C%20Apple's%20margins%20could%20take%20a%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-trump-tariffs-china-liberation-day-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743683336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee76a469253ccddf9b1e98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-trump-tariffs-china-liberation-day-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20impact%20some%20of%20Apple's%20key%20manufacturing%20hubs%2C%20including%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchowdhury%40insider.com%20(Hasan%20Chowdhury)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus