r%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20secular%20parties%20like%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20to%20support%20the%20contentious%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20political%20circles.%20But%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20it%20was%20BJP's%20efforts%20to%20secure%20support%20on%20contentious%20issues%20from%20coalition%20partners%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20JD(U)%20-%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20Muslim%20support%20--%20have%20taken%20a%20stance%20at%20variance%20from%20the%20BJP%20on%20issues%20concerning%20Muslims%2C%20especially%20on%20matters%20like%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%20But%20behind-the-scenes%20discussions%20have%20led%20the%20BJP%20to%20convince%20these%20parties%20to%20support%20the%20bill%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20introducing%20the%20bill%20in%20August%2C%20senior%20ministers%20had%20informed%20the%20TDP%20and%20JD(U)%20leadership%20about%20its%20importance.%20They%20also%20consulted%20leaders%20from%20allies%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20explaining%20its%20necessity%20and%20emphasizing%20that%20it%20aimed%20to%20protect%20Muslim%20interests%20and%20ensure%20women's%20rights%2C%20rather%20than%20polarise%20communities%20as%20the%20Opposition%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20allies%20agreed%20with%20the%20broad%20outline%2C%20they%20had%20concerns%20about%20certain%20provisions%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20impact%20on%20existing%20Waqf%20properties%20and%20encroachment%20on%20state%20governments'%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20bill%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%2C%20which%20accepted%2014%20amendments%20that%20included%20significant%20suggestions%20from%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20TDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%20emphasised%20that%20the%20new%20law%20should%20not%20be%20applied%20retrospectively%20to%20avoid%20interference%20with%20existing%20mosques%2C%20shrines%2C%20or%20other%20Muslim%20religious%20sites.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20insisted%20on%20consulting%20states%20regarding%20decisions%20on%20Waqf%20land%2C%20as%20land%20is%20a%20state%20subject.%20The%20TDP%20advocated%20for%20maintaining%20states'%20autonomy%20and%20suggested%20appointing%20senior%20officials%20above%20the%20collector%20level%20for%20dispute%20resolution%20and%20extending%20the%20timeline%20for%20uploading%20Waqf-related%20documents%20on%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20bill%20incorporated%20these%20suggestions%2C%20leading%20to%20its%20approval%20by%20the%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20TDP%20have%20expressed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20bill%2C%20highlighting%20its%20alignment%20with%20Muslim%20women's%20and%20marginalized%20communities'%20interests.%20The%20LJP%20and%20RLD%20have%20also%20backed%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20met%20JD(U)%20leaders%20Lallan%20Singh%20and%20Sanjay%20Jha%20at%20Parliament%20House%2C%20informing%20them%20that%20the%20party's%20suggestions%20had%20been%20incorporated%20into%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20debate%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%20strongly%20supported%20the%20bill%2C%20dismissing%20concerns%20that%20it%20was%20against%20Muslim%20interests.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20Muslims%2C%20referencing%20them%20multiple%20times%20in%20light%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Bihar%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20TDP's%20KP%20Tenneti%20emphasised%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20had%20made%20several%20decisions%20benefiting%20Muslims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20supported%20the%20bill%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20interests%20of%20Muslim%20women%2C%20youth%2C%20and%20marginalised%20communities.%20Other%20BJP%20allies%2C%20including%20LJP%2C%20Hindustan%20Awam%20Morcha%2C%20and%20the%20RLD%2C%20also%20aligned%20with%20this%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20allies%20on%20board%20on%20the%20bill%20reflects%20the%20continuity%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20style%20from%20his%20second%20to%20third%20term%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743683100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2Fo0v34158_narendra-modi-amit-shah-jp-nadda-pti_625x300_03_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-bjp-brought-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-on-board-for-waqf-bill-8078605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20of%20secular%20parties%20like%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20to%20support%20the%20contentious%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20in%20political%20circles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-bjp-brought-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-on-board-for-waqf-bill-8078605%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'100%20choohe%20kha%20kar%20billi%20Haj%20ko%20chali'%3A%20Giriraj%20Singh%20slams%20Cong%20on%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743682711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119944619%2Cimgsize-1189539.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F100-choohe-kha-kar-billi-haj-ko-chali-bjps-giriraj-singh-slams-congress-on-waqf-bill%2Farticleshow%2F119944561.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%20sharply%20criticized%20Congress%20over%20the%20W