%20Want%20To%20Know%20About%20Waqf%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20Lok%20Sabha%20clearing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20late%20last%20night%20after%20a%20marathon%20debate%2C%20the%20proposed%20law%20is%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20becoming%20an%20Act.%20While%20the%20Centre%20stresses%20that%20the%20changes%20will%20make%20the%20functioning%20of%20Waqf%20Boards%20more%20efficient%2C%20inclusive%20and%20transparent%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20alleged%20that%20it%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20minorities%20and%20that%20the%20government%20is%20eyeing%20the%209.4%20lakh%20acres%20of%20Waqf%20land.%20NDTV%20breaks%20down%20what%20changes%20in%20the%20new%20law%20and%20why%20it%20has%20drawn%20protests%20from%20the%20Opposition%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Waqf%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20'waqf'%20originates%20from%20the%20Arabic%20word%20%26quot%3Bwaqufa%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bto%20hold%26quot%3B.%20Waqf%20refers%20to%20properties%20dedicated%20exclusively%20for%20Muslim%20charitable%20purposes.%20Any%20other%20use%20of%20the%20property%20and%20its%20sale%20are%20prohibited.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20property%20is%20transferred%20to%20Allah.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20donor%20cannot%20reclaim%20a%20Waqf%20property.%20The%20history%20of%20Waqf%20in%20India%20goes%20back%20to%20the%2012th%20Century%3A%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Sultanate.%20Sultan%20Muizuddin%20Sam%20Ghaor%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Muhammad%20of%20Ghori%2C%20had%20dedicated%20two%20villages%20to%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20Multan%20(now%20in%20Pakistan).%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20grew.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20Century%2C%20a%20Waqf%20property%20dispute%20from%20British-ruled%20India%20reached%20the%20Privy%20Council%20of%20London.%20The%20judges%20described%20Waqf%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20perpetuity%20of%20the%20worst%20and%20the%20most%20pernicious%20kind%26quot%3B%20and%20declared%20it%20invalid.%20The%20decision%20was%20not%20accepted%20in%20India%2C%20and%20a%201913%20law%20saved%20the%20institution.%20Since%20then%2C%20no%20attempt%20to%20abolish%20Waqf%20has%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fcfgc7ing_waqf-panel_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Courtesy%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Much%20Property%20Does%20Waqf%20Hold%20In%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20Board%20is%20the%20largest%20landowner%20in%20India%20after%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20and%20the%20Railways.%20According%20to%20the%20Minority%20Affairs%20Ministry%2C%20Waqf%20boards%20control%208.7%20lakh%20properties%20across%20the%20country%2C%20spanning%20about%209.4%20lakh%20acres%20of%20land.%20The%20estimated%20value%20of%20these%20properties%20is%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore.%20There%20are%203%2C56%2C051%20Waqf%20estates%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Of%20the%208%2C72%2C328%20immovable%20properties%20registered%20under%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20over%201.2%20lakh%20are%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Waqf%20boards%20hold%2016%2C713%20movable%20properties%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20maintains%20that%20many%20Waqf%20properties%20face%20major%20disputes%20and%20issues%20such%20as%20encroachment.%20In%20fact%2C%2040%2C951%20cases%20concerning%20these%20properties%20are%20pending%20in%20Tribunals%20and%20nearly%2010%2C000%20of%20them%20are%20filed%20by%20Muslims%20against%20the%20institutions%20managing%20Waqf.%20There%20is%20no%20provision%20under%20the%20current%20law%20for%20these%20disputes%20to%20move%20to%20court%20and%20this%20leads%20to%20delays%20in%20resolution%2C%20the%20Centre%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fvdlko5uc_jama-masjid-delhi-istock_625x300_24_November_22.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonuments%20And%20Waqf%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20Delhi%20is%20a%20Waqf%20property%20managed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board.%20The%20erstwhile%20Mughal%20capital%20of%20Fatehpur%20Sikri%2C%20including%20the%20Tomb%20of%20Salim%20Chishti%2C%20is%20registered%20as%20a%20Waqf%20property.%20The%20Bada%20Imambara%20in%20Lucknow%20is%20also%20a%20Waqf%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20monuments%2C%20Waqf%20ownership%20leads%20to%20administrative%20disputes%20with%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Sunni%20Waqf%20Board%20had%20claimed%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20as%20a%20Waqf%20property.%20The%20ASI%20controls%20the%20monument%20and%20contested%20this%20claim.%20The%20matter%20reached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20asked%20the%20Waqf%20board%20to%20provide%20documentary%20evidence%20to%20support%20their%20claim%2C%20which%20they%20failed%20to%20do.%20Among%20the%20protected%20monuments%20in%20Delhi%20claimed%20by%20Waqf%20boards%20are%20the%20Safdarjung%20Tomb%2C%20Purana%20Qila%2C%20Nila%20Gumbaz%20and%20Isa%20Khan's%20mosque%20(inside%20the%20Humayun's%20Tomb%20complex)%20and%20the%20Jamali%20Kamali%20mosque%20and%20tomb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20temple%20at%20Thiruchenthurai%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20also%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20property%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20temple%20at%20Thiruchenthurai%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20also%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20property%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ftl3jqdfg_tn-temple_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20at%20Thiruchenthurai%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20also%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20property%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20Waqf%20Complications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20residents%20of%20Thiruchenthurai%20village%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20were%20shocked%20to%20know%20that%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Waqf%20board%20had%20claimed%20their%20village%20as%20its%20property.%20The%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20a%20farmer%2C%20Rajagopal%2C%20tried%20to%20sell%20his%201.2-acre%20plot%20and%20authorities%20told%20him%20to%20get%20an%20NOC%20(No%20Objection%20Certificate)%20from%20the%20Waqf%20board.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20tense%20situation%20in%20the%20Hindu-dominated%20village%20as%20residents%20found%20that%20a%201%2C500-year-old%20temple%20in%20the%20village%20was%20also%20tagged%20as%20Waqf%20property.%20The%20state%20Waqf%20board%20demanded%20a%20survey%2C%20but%20this%20has%20not%20been%20carried%20out%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20a%20plot%20owner%20at%20a%20residential%20society%20in%20Gujarat's%20Surat%20registered%20his%20plot%20with%20the%20state%20Waqf%20board%20and%20people%20started%20offering%20namaz%20there.%20%26quot%3BThis%20implied%20that%20an%20apartment%20in%20any%20housing%20society%20can%20any%20day%20turn%20into%20a%20mosque%20without%20any%20input%20from%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20society%20if%20the%20owner%20of%20that%20apartment%20decides%20to%20endow%20it%20as%20Waqf%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20central%20government%20said%2C%20stressing%20the%20need%20to%20amend%20Waqf%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fkgendh98_kiren-rijiju_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Changes%20In%20The%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bill%20aims%20to%20make%20significant%20changes%20to%20the%20existing%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnly%20a%20person%20practising%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20may%20declare%20a%20waqf%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20person%20declaring%20a%20property%20as%20Waqf%20must%20own%20it%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Bill%20removes%20the%20provision%20of%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%20in%20the%20current%20law%2C%20under%20which%20properties%20could%20be%20deemed%20as%20Waqf%20solely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20prolonged%20use%20for%20religious%20purposes.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Waqf%20declaration%20must%20not%20lead%20to%20the%20denial%20of%20inheritance%20rights%20of%20the%20donor's%20heir%2C%20including%20women%20heirs%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAny%20government%20property%20identified%20as%20Waqf%20will%20cease%20to%20be%20so.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERemoves%20Waqf%20board's%20power%20to%20inquire%20and%20determine%20if%20a%20property%20is%20Waqf.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20also%20proposes%20changes%20to%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20and%20Waqf%20boards.%20The%201995%20Waqf%20Act%20requires%20that%20all%20Council%20members%20be%20Muslims%2C%20and%20at%20least%20two%20must%20be%20women.%20The%20new%20bill%20states%20that%20two%20members%20must%20be%20non-Muslims%20and%20of%20the%20Muslim%20members%2C%20two%20must%20be%20women.%20For%20Waqf%20boards%2C%20the%20Bill%20empowers%20the%20state%20government%20to%20nominate%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20or%20MLCs%20to%20the%20board%20and%20these%20nominees%20need%20not%20be%20Muslims.%20The%20bill%20also%20provides%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20representatives%20of%20Bohra%20and%20Agakhani%20communities%2C%20if%20they%20have%20Waqf%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Act%20provides%20that%20at%20least%20two%20board%20members%20must%20be%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Act%2C%20decisions%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Tribunal%20are%20final%20and%20cannot%20be%20challenged%20in%20courts.%20The%20Bill%20changes%20this.%20The%20tribunal's%20orders%20can%20be%20appealed%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20within%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinority%20affairs%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20who%20introduced%20the%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%2C%20has%20said%20crores%20of%20poor%C2%A0Muslims%20will%20thank%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20once%20it%20becomes%20a%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fhajdaef_owaisi_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Protests%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslim%20organisations%20led%20by%20the%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20have%20opposed%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20alleging%20that%20IT%20IS%20based%20on%20discrimination%20and%20injustice%20and%20violates%20fundamental%20rights.%20The%20AIMPLB%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20aims%20to%20use%20the%20bill%20to%20seize%20and%20destroy%20Waqf%20properties.%20%26quot%3BEven%20with%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20searching%20for%20temples%20in%20every%20mosque%20is%20continuously%20escalating.%20If%20this%20amendment%20is%20passed%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20surge%20in%20illegitimate%20governmental%20and%20non-governmental%20claims%20on%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20making%20it%20easier