0data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286bd9c11-c596-4fcc-9877-3f528214960b%5C%22%3EMariana%20Mazzucato%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20tariffs%20will%20cause%20inflation%20in%20the%20United%20States%3B%20they%20will%20cause%20lower%20consumer%20power%20of%20US%20workers.%20The%20estimates%20are%20between%20%241%2C700%20to%20%245%2C000%20per%20family%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20these%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20economics%20professor%20at%20University%20College%20London%20told%20ITV's%20%26quot%3BPeston%26quot%3B%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228dfe1b97-b55b-4b00-b66b-161ecc7c1ef9%5C%22%3EBoaz%20Weinstein%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saba%20Capital%20Management%20founder%20doesn't%20expect%20Trump%20to%20change%20course%2C%20posting%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20often%20wrong%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20him%20doing%20a%20u-turn.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20buy-the-dip%20opportunity.%20It's%20a%20sell%20the%20dip%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c47d4b7-873f-40f6-8075-b0592a95da5e%5C%22%3EDavid%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20this%20tariff%20file%20is%20now%20being%20labeled%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Wealthy%20Again%26quot%3B%3F%20What%20is%20with%20that%20adverb%20%26quot%3Bagain%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20defined%20as%20%26quot%3Breturning%20to%20a%20previous%20condition%26quot%3B%3F%20The%20previous%20condition%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20you%2C%20was%20not%20nearly%20as%20good%20as%20the%20current%20condition%2C%20seeing%20as%20US%20net%20national%20net%20worth%20just%20reached%20a%20record%20level%20of%20%24157%20TRILLION%20(a%20cool%20%241.2%20million%20per%20household%20%E2%80%A6%20too%20bad%20we%20don't%20all%20live%20at%20the%20average!)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20founder%20and%20president%20of%20Rosenberg%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20tariffs%20really%20stood%20in%20the%20way%20of%20wealth%20creation%20in%20America%3F%20I%20think%20the%20title%20should%20simply%20be%20the%20truth%3A%20%26quot%3BLet's%20Make%20the%20World%20Poor%20Again%26quot%3B%20(and%20then%20we%20can%20buy%20it%20at%20a%20discount)%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e38514c5-be7e-435e-bf5a-cb69441f624f%5C%22%3ENouriel%20Roubini%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20the%20NYU%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20label%20was%20%26quot%3BOrwellian%20doublespeak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20the%20consequences%20of%20these%20tariffs%20will%20be%20%E2%80%94%20ie%20lower%20growth%20and%20higher%20inflation%20and%20how%20much%20of%20it%20depending%20on%20the%20eventual%20size%20of%20these%20tariffs%20post-negotiations%20that%20will%20be%20ugly%20and%20long-drawn.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20%26quot%3Bliberation%26quot%3B%20at%20all%20in%20them%3A%20not%20for%20US%20consumers%2C%20workers%20and%20businesses%2C%20let%20alone%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c54599bf-68f4-4a4f-803a-bab033903d9b%5C%22%3EPaul%20Krugman%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20it's%20just%20possible%20that%20when%20we%20get%20details%20about%20the%20Trump%20tariffs%20they%20will%20be%20lower%20than%20what%20he%20just%20announced%2C%20but%20based%20on%20what%20he%20said%2C%20he's%20gone%20full-on%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Krugman%2C%20Nobel-winning%20economist%20and%20former%20MIT%20and%20Princeton%20University%20professor%20wrote%20on%20Substack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20had%20any%20hopes%20that%20Trump%20would%20step%20back%20from%20the%20brink%2C%20this%20announcement%2C%20between%20the%20very%20high%20tariff%20rates%20and%20the%20complete%20falsehoods%20about%20what%20other%20countries%20do%2C%20should%20kill%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Krugman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftru