20arrested%20for%20smuggling%20gold%20into%20the%20country%2C%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20hawala%20racket%20amounting%20to%20over%20Rs%2038%20crore%2C%20investigators%20have%20said.%C2%A0NDTV%20has%20accessed%20a%20remand%20copy%20of%20Sahil%20Jain%2C%20the%20accused%20number%203%20in%20the%20case.%20This%20document%20has%20shocking%20details%20of%20how%20he%20and%20Ranya%20Rao%20did%20not%20just%20smuggle%20gold%20from%20Dubai%2C%20but%20allegedly%20moved%20money%20through%20hawala%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20her%20close%20aide%20Tarun%20Raju%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection%20and%20is%20the%20second%20accused.%20Sahil%20Jain%2C%20the%20third%20accused%2C%20is%20a%20gold%20merchant%20who%20allegedly%20helped%20her%20dispose%20of%20the%20smuggled%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20investigators%2C%20Sahil%20has%20said%20he%20assisted%20and%20abetted%20%26quot%3BA1%26quot%3B%20--%20accused%20No%201%20Ranya%20Rao%20--%20in%20disposing%20of%2014%20kg%20gold%20worth%20Rs%2011.5%20crore%20in%20January.%20He%20has%20also%20said%20he%20helped%20her%20move%20hawala%20money%20worth%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20in%20Bengaluru.%20According%20to%20the%20remand%20copy%2C%20Sahil%20has%20also%20told%20the%20investigators%20that%20he%20helped%20Ranya%20Rao%20dispose%2013%20kg%20gold%20worth%20Rs%2011.8%20crore%20and%20hawala%20money%20worth%20Rs%2011.25%20crore%20to%20Dubai%20in%20February.%20He%20also%20assisted%20her%20in%20moving%20hawala%20money%20worth%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20to%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigators%20have%20said%20that%20Sahil%20helped%20Ranya%20Rao%20dispose%20of%20a%20total%20of%20nearly%2050%20kg%20gold%20worth%20around%20Rs%2040%20crore%20and%20hawala%20cash%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2038%20crore%20between%20Dubai%20and%20Bengaluru.%20He%20has%20said%20he%20was%20receiving%20a%20commission%20of%20Rs%2055%2C000%20for%20each%20of%20these%20transactions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20r