0that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229475273b-1f3f-459c-9f32-3a05f7a30ea1%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20tariffs%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tariff%20is%20effectively%20a%20government%20tax%20specifically%20levied%20on%20foreign%20goods%20imported%20into%20a%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20increase%20the%20cost%20of%20foreign%20products%2C%20making%20them%20less%20competitive%20compared%20to%20domestic%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernments%20use%20tariffs%20to%20raise%20revenue%20and%20protect%20local%20industries%20from%20foreign%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Trump's%20new%20tariff%20plan%2C%20China%20will%20face%20a%2034%25%20tariff%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2020%25%2C%20Taiwan%2032%25%2C%20and%20India%2026%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20primarily%20targets%20countries%20with%20whom%20the%20US%20has%20the%20highest%20trade%20deficits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c93bed01-9ff6-4391-a03d-0a82bfdd000a%5C%22%3EWho%20pays%20them%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EImporters%20are%20responsible%20for%20paying%20tariffs%20when%20goods%20enter%20the%20US%2C%20but%20these%20costs%20are%20often%20passed%20on%20to%20consumers%20through%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20exporting%20countries%20don't%20directly%20pay%20tariffs%2C%20the%20increased%20prices%20may%20make%20their%20goods%20less%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20insisted%20that%20his%20trade%20policies%20would%20bring%20in%20revenue%20and%20restore%20jobs%2C%20but%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113934450227067577%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eacknowledged%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20February%20Truth%20Social%20post%20that%20Americans%20would%20feel%20%26quot%3Bsome%20pain%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259cfdcaf-491c-4cc7-9a33-1fabd3535d6d%5C%22%3EWhen%20do%20Trump's%20tariffs%20go%20into%20effect%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20baseline%2010%25%20tariff%20is%20set%20to%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20April%205%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20E.T.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20rates%20for%20specific%20countries%20will%20come%20into%20force%20on%20April%209%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20E.T.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e20b291f-02e2-44d9-8902-3396d013f99e%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20Trump%20putting%20tariffs%20on%20other%20countries%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20executive%20order%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20tariffs%20are%20necessary%20to%20correct%20trade%20imbalances%20and%20protect%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20large%20trade%20deficits%20have%20eroded%20the%20US%20manufacturing%20industry%20and%20left%20supply%20chains%20vulnerable%20to%20foreign%20influence%2C%20which%20he%20views%20as%20detrimental%20to%20the%20country's%20economic%20and%20strategic%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20situation%20is%20evidenced%20by%20disparate%20tariff%20rates%20and%20non-tariff%20barriers%20that%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20US%20manufacturers%20to%20sell%20their%20products%20in%20foreign%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bf75b1f-3414-44c8-96e6-c507406bb2e2%5C%22%3EWill%20prices%20go%20up%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20said%20that%20tariffs%20will%20eventually%20lower%20prices%20for%20Americans%2C%20but%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20their%20implementation%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthink.ing.com%2Farticles%2Fbeautiful-tariffs-risk-turning-the-growth-outlook-ugly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kcl.ac.uk%2Ftrumps-tariffs-what-is-behind-them-and-will-they-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elead%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20several%20companies%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20would%20raise%20prices%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-trump-tariffs-inflation-goods-getting-more-expensive-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%20increased%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20importers%20often%20pass%20on%20additional%20costs%20to%20buyers%2C%20goods%20subject%20to%20tariffs%20will%20likely%20become%20more%20expensive%2C%20contributing%20to%20overall%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20Boston%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bostonfed.org%2Fpublications%2Fcurrent-policy-perspectives%2F2025%2Fthe-impact-of-tariffs-on-inflation.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%2060%25%20tariff%20in%20China%20and%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20would%20increase%20inflation%20by%20between%201.4%20and%202.2%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2F-%2Fmedia%2FFiles%2FPublications%2FWEO%2F2024%2FOctober%2FEnglish%2Fch1.ashx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%20that%20if%20the%20US%2C%20the%20eurozone%2C%20and%20China%20imposed%2010%25%20tariffs%2C%20the%20US%20GDP%20could%20shrink%20by%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd85787e-9324-4912-8f3c-fa77af3b9fc6%5C%22%3EWhat%20will%20happen%20with%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20on%20employment%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20may%20create%20jobs%20in%20protected%20industries%20like%20steel%20and%20manufacturing%20but%20could%20also%20result%20in%20job%20losses%20in%20sectors%20that%20rely%20on%20imported%20materials%20or%20face%20foreign%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20March%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.richmondfed.org%2Fresearch%2Fnational_economy%2Fcfo_survey%2Fdata_and_results%2F2025%2F20250326_data_and_results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Duke%20University%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Banks%20of%20Richmond%20and%20Atlanta%2C%20one%20in%20four%20US%20businesses%20believed%20that%20trade%20policy%20changes%20would%20negatively%20impact%20their%20hiring%20plans%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-trump-tariffs-work-what-are-tariffs-trump-plan-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743678223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ee568f69253ccddf9b1c1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-trump-tariffs-work-what-are-tariffs-trump-plan-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20imposed%20a%20slew%20of%20tariffs%20ranging%20from%2010%20to%2049%25%20on%20trading%20partners.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%2C%20who%20pays%20them%2C%20and%20how%20they%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-trump-tariffs-work-what-are-tariffs-trump-plan-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20a%20Saree%20%26amp%3B%20Solar%20Power%2C%20He%E2%80%99s%20Bringing%20Safe%20Drinking%20Water%20To%20400%2B%20Children%20In%20Rural%20Schools%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20walking%20into%20a%20rural%20school%2C%20where%20young%20children%20sip%20from%20a%20community%20water%20tank%2C%20unaware%20of%20the%20microscopic%20dangers%20lurking%20within.%20For%20years%2C%20the%20water%20they%20consumed%20unknowingly%20became%20a%20conduit%20for%20diseases%20like%20diarrhoea%20and%20typhoid%20%E2%80%94%20ailments%20that%20not%20only%20ravaged%20their%20health%20but%20also%20hampered%20their%20cognitive%20development.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20gut-brain%20connection%20that%20influences%20lifelong%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20plight%20of%20school-going%20children%20in%20Phaltan%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20