ked%20the%20School%20Service%20Commission%20to%20repeat%20the%20recruitment%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20upheld%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%2C%20cancelling%20the%20appointment%20of%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20teachers%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20under%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20entire%20selection%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Bvitiated%20by%20manipulation%20and%20fraud%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20%26quot%3Bdenuded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20PV%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20said%20that%20it%20saw%20no%20reason%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20High%20Court%20order.%20The%20court%20said%20the%20appointments%20resulted%20from%20cheating%20and%20are%20thus%20fraudulent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20aspect%20of%20the%20judgment%20is%20that%20those%20appointed%20through%20fair%20means%20have%20also%20suffered%20like%20the%20tainted%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaking%20this%20up%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20asked%20why%20so%20many%20people%20must%20be%20punished%20for%20a%20few.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%2025%2C000%20candidates%2C%20their%20families%20are%20impacted%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20huge%20case%20recovery%20from%20the%20residence%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20judge%20Yashwant%20Varma%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20recover%20money%20from%20a%20sitting%20judge's%20home%2C%20he%20is%20only%20transferred.%20Then%20why%20were%20these%20candidates%20not%20transferred%3F%20The%20first%20judge%20to%20give%20this%20order%20is%20now%20a%20BJP%20MP.%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20have%20conspired%20to%20lead%20to%20this%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20target%20Bengal%2C%20she%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20a%20crime%20to%20be%20born%20in%20the%20state.%20She%20questioned%20who%20would%20teach%20in%20classrooms%20if%20so%20many%20teachers%20lost%20their%20jobs.%20She%20said%20over%2011%2C000%20of%20the%20affected%20teachers%20taught%20in%20Class%209%20and%2010%20and%20over%205%2C500%20in%20Class%2011%20and%2012.%20%26quot%3BClass%209-12%20are%20very%20important%20classes%2C%20the%20gateway%20to%20higher%20education.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20correcting%20answer%20sheets%20of%20board%20exams.%20Do%20BJP%20and%20CPM%20want%20the%20education%20system%20to%20collapse%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743676920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fduniggqo_mamata-banerjee_625x300_06_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-accept-verdict-personally-mamata-banerjee-on-court-order-sacking-25-000-teachers-8077265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Accept%20Verdict%20Personally%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20On%20Court%20Order%20Sacking%2025%2C000%20Teachers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-accept-verdict-personally-mamata-banerjee-on-court-order-sacking-25-000-teachers-8077265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Fardeen%20Khan%20addressed%20feud%20with%20Shahid%20Kapoor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743676618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119941691%2Cimgsize-43424.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwhen-fardeen-khan-addressed-feud-with-shahid-kapoor-due-to-do-link-up-rumours-with-kareena-kapoor-khan-i-heard-he-was-btching-about-me%2Farticleshow%2F119941716.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119941716.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%22