that%20I'm%20proud%20of%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20clinked%20his%20wine%20glass%20against%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20my%20acceptance%20letter%20a%20week%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20learning%20to%20trust%20that%20when%20he%20says%20our%20marriage%20and%20family%20are%20his%20first%20priority%2C%20he%20means%20it%20because%20his%20actions%20reveal%20his%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20preparing%20for%20him%20to%20be%20gone%20on%20future%20trips%2C%20he's%20been%20working%20on%20moving%20his%20GI%20Bill%20educational%20benefits%20to%20help%20fund%20my%20graduate%20school%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20figuring%20out%20what%20it%20means%20to%20have%20a%20successful%20marriage%20while%20navigating%20military%20demands%2C%20but%20we're%20committed%20to%20making%20our%20partnership%20work%20so%20we%20can%20both%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-military-husband-thrived-i-crumbled-depression-anxiety-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743675182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5b22db8b41a9673fbebde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-military-husband-thrived-i-crumbled-depression-anxiety-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brittany%20Meng%20and%20her%20husband%20had%20a%20solid%20marriage%2C%20but%20that%20changed%20when%20he%20joined%20the%20military%20and%20Brittany%20had%20to%20let%20go%20of%20her%20dreams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Brittany%20A.%20Meng)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-military-husband-thrived-i-crumbled-depression-anxiety-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SKY%20Quitting%20Mumbai%20To%20Join%20Goa%3F%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20Breaks%20Silence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3C