Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20India%20stars%20flopped%20on%20their%20domestic%20return%2C%20with%C2%A0Jaiswal%C2%A0scoring%204%20and%2026%20as%20Mumbai%20lost%20by%20five%20wickets%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20the%20tournament's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743674940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fivk3qsbg_suryakumar-yadav-bcci_625x300_01_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsuryakumar-yadav-quitting-mumbai-to-join-goa-mumbai-cricket-association-breaks-silence-8077396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20reports%20suggested%20that%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20T20I%20captain%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20was%20in%20talks%20with%20Goa%20off%20a%20possible%20switch%20from%20Mumbai%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsuryakumar-yadav-quitting-mumbai-to-join-goa-mumbai-cricket-association-breaks-silence-8077396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2218%20And%20Ticking%3A%20The%20Booming%20IPL%20Business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20demure%20bride%20keeps%20her%20veil%20on%20the%20whole%20day%2C%20despite%20coaxing%20from%20in-laws.%20She%20won't%20budge%2C%20not%20even%20for%20her%20new%20husband.%20Enter%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20and%20the%20veil%20is%20gone%2C%20revealing%20a%20star-struck%2C%20wide-eyed%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20sees%20the%20number%2018%20all%20around%20him%20at%20a%20cafe%20and%20is%20baffled.%20Then%20viewers%20learn%20it's%20the%2018th%20season%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20and%20Bengaluru%20(Kohli's%20IPL%20team)%20has%20its%20sights%20set%20on%20the%20title%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20'manoranjan%20ka%20baap'%20(big%20daddy%20of%20entertainment)%20in%202008%20to%20'sabka%20level%20up%20hoga'%20(everyone%20will%20up%20their%20game)%2C%20IPL%20is%20raking%20in%20the%20moolah%20and%20grabbing%20eyeballs%20all%20the%20way.%20In%20its%20opening%20weekend%20(March%2022-23%2C%202025)%2C%20IPL%20viewership%20showed%20a%20whopping%2040%25%20year-on-year%20growth%20with%20137%20crore%20views%2C%20according%20to%20Jio%20Hotstar%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20exclusive%20domestic%20digital%20broadcasting%20rights%20for%20the%20League%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%202023-2027%20cycle.%20Peak%20concurrent%20views%20were%20at%203.4%20crore.%20For%20perspective%2C%20that%20is%20Delhi's%20population.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIPL's%20phenomenal%20growth%20shows%20in%20some%20dizzying%20numbers.%20BARC%20(Broadcast%20Audience%20Research%20Council%2C%20India)%20data%20shows%20for%20three%20years%20-%202016%2C%202017%20and%202018%20-%20viewership%20of%20General%20Entertainment%20Channels%20fell%20by%201-3%20per%20cent%20during%20IPL%20weeks.%20For%20news%20channels%2C%20viewership%20fell%20by%202%20per%20cent%20in%202017%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIPL%20telecast%20has%20shown%20significant%20impact%20on%20viewing%20habits%20for%20other%20genres%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20BARC's%202018%20newsletter.%20%26quot%3BThe%20share%20of%20GEC%20genre%20declined%20marginally%20in%20all%20three%20years%20(2016%2C%202017%20and%202018)%2C%20as%20viewers%20tuned%20into%20IPL%20matches%20during%20prime%20time%20when%20general%20entertainment%20content%20otherwise%20ruled%20the%20roost%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECricketainment.%20How%20did%20it%20come%20to%20this%3F%20A%20cricket-crazy%20nation%2C%20a%20galaxy%20of%20sponsors%20and%20a%20marketing%20blitzkrieg%20-%20a%20potent%20combination%20that%20has%20kept%20the%20IPL%20soaring%20for%2018%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202008%2C%20T20%20was%20not%20even%20considered%20serious%20cricket.%20Though%20India%20had%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202007%2C%20the%20traditional%20formats%20(ODI%20and%20Test)%20still%20scored%20with%20the%20audience.%20But%20much%20has%20changed%20since---the%20three%20editions%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%20(2010%2C%202014%2C%202022)%2C%20which%20had%20the%20T20%20as%20an%20integral%20component%3B%20its%20re-introduction%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%202022%20after%2024%20years%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20return%20of%20cricket%20in%20the%20Olympics%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20in%202028%20after%20128%20years%2C%20probably%20in%20its%20T20%20avatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET20%20franchises%20are%20now%20more%20serious%20in%20year-long%20functions%20than%20just%20setting%20shop%20for%20two%20months%20of%20IPL.%20Among%20the%2010%20IPL%20teams%2C%20eight%20either%20have%20stakes%20or%20own%20teams%20in%20foreign%20franchise%20leagues%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20West%20Indies%2C%20England%20and%20the%20USA.%20The%20IPL%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20the%20crown%20jewel.%20A%20stake%20in%20an%20IPL%20team%20is%20a%20big%20business%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Prime%20Property%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20for%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20generated%20revenues%20of%20Rs%2020%2C686%20crore%20last%20year.%20The%20BCCI%20is%20the%20world's%20richest%20cricket%20board.%20Though%20T20%20franchise%20leagues%20are%20mushrooming%20around%20the%20world%2C%20no%20active%20Indian%20player%20is%20allowed%20in%20foreign%20leagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20restricted%20to%20domestic%20players.%20The%20fat%20paycheques%20ensure%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20best%20of%20foreign%20talent%20for%20two%20months%20on%20Indian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20cricketing%20best%20have%20congregated%20once%20again%20for%20the%20prime-time%20audience.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIPL%20has%20been%20a%20crowd-puller%20ever%20since%20its%20launch.%20In%20fact%2C%20according%20to%20BARC%20data%2C%2035%20crore%20viewers%20watched%20the%20live%20broadcast%20of%20the%20first%2010%20IPL%20matches%20on%20television%20in%202024%2C%20higher%20than%20any%20previous%20edition%20of%20the%20league%2C%20including%20seasons%20played%20during%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIPL's%20annual%20broadcast%20revenues%20are%20on%20par%20with%20top%20global%20sporting%20leagues%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20game-changer%20of%20IPL%20has%20been%20the%20streaming%20platforms.%20While%20Star%20had%20the%20telecast%20rights%20for%20IPL%20on%20its%20Hotstar%20app%20from%202015%2C%20the%20story%20took%20an%20altogether%20new%20turn%20when%20Viacom18%20(its%20streaming%20platform%20was%20called%20Jio%20Cinema%20then)%20acquired%20the%20digital%20rights%20for%20the%202023-2027%20cycle%20for%20Rs%2023%2C758%20crore.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20digital%20rights%20were%20sold%20at%20a%20higher%20price%20than%20TV%20rights%2C%20won%20by%20Disney%20Star%20for%20Rs%2023%2C575%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJio%20Cinema's%20decision%20to%20broadcast%20IPL%20for%20free%20in%202023%20and%202024%20was%20the%20booster%20shot%20that%20digital%20viewership%20needed.%20The%20digital%20viewership%20of%20IPL%202024%20was%20reportedly%20620%20million%20(Jio%20Cinema)%20and%20the%20TV%20viewership%20was%20546%20million%20(Star%20Sports%20TV).%20%C2%A0So%20hooked%20are%20viewers%20that%20after%20the%20merger%20of%20Jio%20Cinema%20and%20Hotstar%2C%20IPL%20being%20put%20behind%20a%20paywall%20was%20hardly%20a%20dampener%20for%20India.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0Prioritising%20Matches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20maximise%20viewership%2C%20broadcasters%20have%20chalked%20out%20a%20strategy%20where%20preference%20is%20given%20to%20matches%20involving%20the%20Big%20Four-%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders-during%20promotions.%20Collectively%2C%20these%20four%20sides%20boast%20of%20a%20bigger%20fanbase%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20six%20IPL%20teams%20put%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20first%20three%20matches%2C%20which%20had%20a%20viewership%20of%20137%20crore%2C%20included%20the%20two%20marquee%20games%20of%20KKR%20vs%20RCB%20and%20MI%20vs%20CSK.%20The%20pattern%20follows%20the%20European%20football%20leagues%2C%20where%20an%20El%20Clasico%20in%20La%20Liga%20or%20a%20Manchester%20United%20match%20in%20Premier%20League%20grabs%20more%20eyeballs%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20level%20of%20the%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20tournament%20that%20runs%20for%20over%20two%20months%2C%20with%20matches%20stacked%20up%20non-stop%2C%20fatigue%20can%20set%20in%20among%20viewers.%20Matches%20of%20the%20big%20four%20are%20scheduled%20so%20as%20to%20tackle%20that%20weariness.%20With%20an%20eye%20on%20weekends%2C%20weekdays%20have%20one%20match%20each%2C%20while%20Saturdays%20and%20Sundays%20see%20two%20matches%20per%20day%20for%20most%20of%20the%20IPL%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20IPL%20enters%20'adulthood'%20%C2%A0this%20year%2C%20all%20involved%20will%20hope%20for%20a%20growth%20spurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743674880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Ffhbqrlco_virat-kohli-shah-rukh-khan-ipl-_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F18-and-ticking-the-booming-ipl-business-8077383%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20cricket-crazy%20nation%2C%20a%20galaxy%20of%20sponsors%20and%20a%20marketing%20blitzkrieg%20-%20a%20potent%20combination%20that%20has%20kept%20the%20IPL%20soaring%20for%2018%20seasons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F18-and-ticking-the-booming-ipl-business-8077383%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manoj%20Desai%20slams%20Sikandar%20makers%20for%20killing%20the%20heroine%20so%20e