%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Crist%C3%B3bal%20Tapia%20de%20Veer%2C%20the%20acclaimed%20composer%20of%20%E2%80%9CWhite%20Lotus%E2%80%9Ds%20theme%20song%2C%20said%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20back%20for%20Season%204.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Tapia%20de%20Veer%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Chile%20and%20lives%20in%20Quebec%2C%20said%20they%20had%20different%20visions%20for%20the%20theme%20song%20that%20started%20in%20Season%201%20and%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Elskes%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fwhite-lotus-season-4-mike-white-1236358536%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Trump's%20tariffs%20divert%20FII%20money%20towards%20Indian%20stock%20markets%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743674461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fwill-trump-s-tariffs-divert-fii-money-towards-indian-stock-markets-125040300774_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20Tariffs%3A%20The%20tariff%20news%2C%20analysts%20added%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20perceived%20positively%20by%20both%20domestic%20and%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%2C%20particularly%20in%20export-oriented%20sectors%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fwill-trump-s-tariffs-divert-fii-money-towards-indian-stock-markets-125040300774_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Am%20Free%26quot%3B%3A%20Myanmar%20Teacher%20Pulled%20Out%20Of%20Rubble%205%20Days%20After%20Earthquake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEntombed%20under%20his%20hotel%20bed%20for%20five%20days%20in%20the%20debris%2C%20two%20things%20enabled%20teacher%20Tin%20Maung%20Htwe%20to%20survive%20Myanmar's%20devastating%20earthquake%3A%20old%20school%20lessons%20and%20his%20own%20urine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20school%20headmaster%20was%20on%20a%20training%20course%20in%20Sagaing%2C%20the%20closest%20place%20to%20the%20epicentre%2C%20when%20the%207.7-magnitude%20earthquake%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2047-year-old%20remembered%20a%20decades-old%20school%20lesson%20to%20shelter%20under%20a%20bed%20if%20the%20world%20starts%20to%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20I%20went%20under%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20whole%20hotel%20fell%20down%20and%20was%20blocked.%20All%20I%20could%20afford%20was%20to%20say%20'save%20me'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20shouting%20'save%20me%2C%20save%20me'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Swal%20Taw%20Nann%20guesthouse%20where%20he%20was%20staying%20was%20reduced%20to%20a%20pile%20of%20bricks%20and%20twisted%20metal%20strips%2C%20the%20broken%20shell%20of%20its%20top%20storey%20resting%20on%20the%20remains%20of%20those%20below%2C%20and%20Tin%20Maung%20Htwe%20in%20a%20ground%20floor%20room%20underneath%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20was%20in%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20weakly%2C%20an%20oxygen%20tube%20running%20to%20his%20nose%20and%20two%20intravenous%20drips%20into%20his%20reduced%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20body%20was%20burning%20hot%20and%20all%20I%20needed%20was%20water.%20I%20couldn't%20get%20that%20water%20from%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20have%20to%20refill%20the%20water%20my%20body%20needed%20with%20fluids%20coming%20out%20of%20my%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20am%20free'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intensity%20of%20destruction%20in%20Sagaing%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20epicentre%2C%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20in%20neighbouring%20Mandalay%2C%20with%20a%20much%20greater%20proportion%20of%20its%20buildings%20reduced%20to%20piles%20of%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreat%20gouges%20have%20been%20opened%20up%20in%20the%20main%20road%20towards%20it%20--%20jamming%20traffic%20and%20hampering%20those%20trying%20to%20help%20the%20victims%20--%20and%20the%20Ava%20bridge%20across%20the%20Irrawaddy%20linking%20the%20two%20cities%20is%20down%2C%20one%20end%20of%20six%20of%20its%2010%20spans%20resting%20in%20the%20placid%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20said%20the%20Myanmar%20Red%20Cross%20were%20recovering%20bodies%20from%20the%20site%20and%20were%20not%20expecting%20to%20find%20anyone%20alive%20when%20they%20located%20him%2C%20and%20a%20Malaysian%20rescue%20team%20was%20called%20in%20to%20extract%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20eight%20siblings%2C%20his%20sister%20Nan%20Yone%2C%2050%2C%20was%20one%20of%20several%20of%20his%20relatives%20watching%20and%20waiting%20as%20they%20worked%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20describe%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nan%20Yone%20of%20his%20rescue%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20dancing%2C%20crying%20and%20beating%20my%20chest%20because%20I%20was%20so%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20arrived%20at%20Sagaing's%20main%20hospital%20he%20gave%20her%20a%20thumbs-up%20and%20told%20her%3A%20%26quot%3BSister%20I%20am%20very%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20will%20is%20very%20strong%20and%20I%20think%20that%20is%20why%20he%20survived%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20the%20day%20he%20was%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20spoke%20nurses%20tended%20to%20her%20semi-conscious%20brother%20on%20a%20outdoor%20gurney%2C%20his%20head%20lolling%20occasionally%20from%20side%20to%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20is%20being%20treated%20indoors%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20for%20fear%20of%20an%20aftershock%20wreaking%20more%20havoc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20I%20am%20free%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Tin%20Maung%20Htwe%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20if%20I%20was%20dead