cts%20with%20health%20systems%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcleveland-clinic-5g-powered-smart-hospital-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECleveland%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tampa%20General%2C%20and%20Nebraska%20Medicine%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20well%20as%20its%20focus%20on%20AI%20at%20a%20time%20when%2C%20as%20Goldstein%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bfolks%20are%20worried%20about%20getting%20left%20behind%2C%20and%20starting%20to%20question%20if%20the%20partnerships%20they%20already%20had%20are%20actually%20creating%20any%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir's%20unfair%20advantage%20in%20healthcare%20is%20obvious%3A%20the%20company%20has%20a%20depth%20of%20resources%20and%20financial%20backing%20at%20its%20fingertips%20rarely%20afforded%20to%20healthcare%20startups%2C%20plus%20the%20software%20capabilities%20to%20build%20personalized%20AI-powered%20solutions%20for%20health%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir%20isn't%20entirely%20pushing%20out%20other%20healthcare%20companies%2C%20however.%20The%20data%20company%20launched%20a%20partnership%20in%20March%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-deals-coming-healthcare-startups-take-privates-private-equity-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ER1%20RCM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20revenue%20cycle%20management%20company%20acquired%20by%20TowerBrook%20and%20CD%26amp%3BR%20in%20a%20%248.9%20billion%20take-private%20deal%20in%20August.%20Palantir%20also%20launched%20a%20program%20called%20HealthStart%20last%20year%20to%20equip%20healthcare%20startups%20with%20tools%20like%20Palantir's%20developer%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20hard%20to%20get%20access%20to%20problems%20in%20healthcare%20because%20of%20the%20monopolistic%20electronic%20medical%20records%20players%20and%20the%20information%20security%20challenges%20of%20working%20with%20patient%20health%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20startup%20teams%20all%20over%20the%20place%20to%20get%20access%20to%20those%20problems%20and%20solve%20them%20faster%2C%20and%20democratize%20that%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20valuable%20for%20the%20whole%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palantir%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f40369c89aff80028ab751c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EArnd%20Wiegmann%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280be2e75-519b-472b-8d98-60664e0ce61a%5C%22%3EHow%20Palantir%20is%20trying%20to%20transform%20healthcare%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir%20kicked%20off%20its%20healthcare%20push%20in%202021%2C%20working%20with%20Cleveland%20Clinic%20and%20Tampa%20General%2C%20when%20Goldstein%20and%20David%20were%20both%2025%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20given%20a%20tall%20task%3A%20promise%20these%20giant%20healthcare%20institutions%20that%2C%20in%20two%20months%2C%20they%20would%20deploy%20Palantir's%20software%20customized%20for%20healthcare%20to%20drive%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we've%20been%20cast%20as%20the%20people%20here%20to%20fix%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20we%20show%20up%20as%20two%2025-year-olds%2C%20it's%20a%20hilarious%20position%20to%20be%20put%20in%20because%20they%20hate%20you%20by%20default%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldstein%20and%20David%2C%20now%2029%20years%20old%2C%20set%20out%20to%20build%20software%20for%20health%20systems%20in%20three%20buckets%3A%20revenue%20cycle%20management%2C%20staffing%20and%20scheduling%2C%20and%20patient%20capacity%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20revenue%20cycle%20management%2C%20Goldstein%20and%20David%20set%20out%20to%20automate%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20how%20hospitals%20capture%20and%20manage%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20from%20coding%20to%20submitting%20claims%20to%20handling%20insurance%20denials.%20They%20decided%20to%20partner%20with%20R1%20RCM%20because%20its%20business%20can%20help%20manage%20the%20whole%20RCM%20process%20on%20top%20of%20Palantir's%20platform.%20In%20contrast%2C%20many%20startups%20are%20only%20able%20to%20tackle%20a%20subset%20of%20revenue%20cycle%20tasks%2C%20Goldstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20workforce%20management%20side%2C%20Palantir%20began%20working%20with%20Nashville-based%20HCA%20Healthcare%20in%202023%20to%20create%20medical%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprovider%20schedules%20with%20AI%2C%20taking%20into%20consideration%20clinicians'%20preferences%20and%20other%20staffing%20constraints.%20Palantir%20says%20it's%20now%20deployed%20its%20customized%20workforce%20management%20software%20across%20about%2075%20of%20the%20health%20system's%20hospitals%20for%20more%20than%2040%2C000%20nurses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Palantir's%20120-person%20strong%20healthcare%20team%20has%20worked%20exclusively%20with%20hospitals%20to%20date%2C%20David%20said%20he%20and%20Goldstein%20have%20been%20having%20more%20conversations%20about%20where%20Palantir%20could%20plug%20into%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system%2C%20like%20by%20helping%20to%20manage%20interactions%20between%20payers%20and%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20automate%20and%20improve%20the%20interface%20between%20the%20payer%20and%20provider%2C%20that%20market%20is%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20and%20no%20one's%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Karp%20in%20a%20purple%20sweather%20talking%20at%20a%20conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6543c1623cc84b4dfafae71f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalantir%20CEO%20Alex%20Karp.%3Cp%3EFabrice%20Coffrini%2FAFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir's%20entry%20into%20heal