times.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fscotch-whisky-association-disappointed-as-us-tariffs-bound-to-take-effect%2Famp_articleshow%2F119935924.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actor%20Jean-Claude%20Van%20Damme%20Accepted%20Sex%20With%205%20Women%20As%20%26quot%3BGift%26quot%3B%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Jean-Claude%20Van%20Damme%20is%20facing%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20in%20Romania%20for%20allegedly%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20relations%20with%20trafficked%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2064-year-old%C2%A0%3Cem%3EStreet%20Fighter%3C%2Fem%3E%20actor%20is%20accused%20of%20accepting%20five%20Romanian%20women%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgift%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20criminal%20network%20led%20by%20Morel%20Bolea%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.antena3.ro%2Factualitate%2Fjean-claude-van-damme-are-plangere-penala-la-diicot-e-acuzat-ca-ar-fi-facut-sex-cu-romance-traficate-de-reteaua-lui-morel-bolea-741280.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%20affiliate%20Antena%203%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomanian%20authorities%20have%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Directorate%20for%20Investigating%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Terrorism%20(DIICOT)%2C%20alleging%20the%2064-year-old%20was%20aware%20the%20women%20were%20victims%20of%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20incident%20reportedly%20took%20place%20in%20Cannes%2C%20France%2C%20during%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20Van%20Damme.%20One%20of%20the%20women%20later%20provided%20testimony%2C%20leading%20DIICOT%20to%20launch%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttorney%20Adrian%20Cuculis%2C%20representing%20one%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20women%20were%20in%20a%20state%20of%20vulnerability%2C%20with%20clear%20indications%20of%20exploitation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSeveral%20Romanians%20under%20investigation%20for%20forming%20a%20criminal%20group%20and%20tra