ves%20across%20rural%20India.%20Her%20decades-long%20efforts%20were%20recently%20recognised%20when%20she%20received%20the%20prestigious%20%E2%80%98Pride%20of%20NID%E2%80%99%20award%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288944%2Fdroupadi-murmu-india-president-candidate-first-from-tribal-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20her%20alma%20mater%2C%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%20(NID)%2C%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShe%20thought%20she%E2%80%99d%20make%20pots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20design%20was%20itself%20an%20act%20of%20defiance.%20After%20her%20family%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20she%20spent%20her%20high%20school%20and%20junior%20college%20years%20fighting%20to%20wear%20trousers%2C%20keep%20short%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%2C%20to%20join%20NID.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20opposed%20it%20because%20it%20was%20only%20a%20diploma%20course%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20NID%2C%20she%20studied%20industrial%20design%2C%20specialising%20in%20ceramic%20design.%20Here%2C%20she%20also%20met%20her%20late%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Rajasthani%20agricultural%20engineer%20who%20came%20to%20NID%20to%20study%20design%20for%20agriculture%20%E2%80%94%20and%20after%20graduation%20in%201986%2C%20moved%20to%20Udaipur.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20373px)%20100vw%2C%20373px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FDr-Lakshmi-with-D