em%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20time%2C%20as%20more%20players%20entered%20the%20market%20and%20disposable%20pads%20flooded%20rural%20areas%2C%20production%20dwindled.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sadness%20for%20me%20comes%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20free%20disposable%20pads%20were%20supplied%20in%20schools%20across%20Rajasthan.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20understand%20it%20is%20a%20rights%20and%20convenience%20issue.%20But%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20environmental%20issue.%20In%20rural%20areas%2C%20there%20is%20no%20proper%20disposal%20system.%20They%20just%20lie%20around%20and%20end%20up%20in%20landfills.%20Even%20so-called%20compostable%20pads%20are%20not%20fully%20compostable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20period%20work%20really%20takes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20years%20alone%2C%20Uger%20and%20Jatan%20Sansthan%20have%20reached%20over%201%2C05%2C000%20individuals%2C%20including%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20boys%20and%20young%20men%2C%20by%20working%20with%2075%20organisations%20across%20India.%20Their%20training%20modules%20%E2%80%94%20also%20designed%20in%20the%20copy%20left%20spirit%20%E2%80%94%20have%20enabled%20numerous%20SHGs%20to%20produce%20and%20distribute%20pads%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202970px)%20100vw%2C%202970px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWomen-stitching-pads_11zon-1-1743519409.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rural%20women%20take%20charge%20of%20menstrual%20health%20by%20stitching%20reusable%20pads%20%E2%80%94%20a%20skill%20taught%20by%20Jatan%20to%20enable%20income%20generation%20and%20improve%20access%20to%20sustainable%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWomen-stitching-pads_1