stand%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20female%20body.%20It%20was%20very%20powerful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarting%20a%20PhD%20at%2050%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%2050s%2C%20Lakshmi%20received%20an%20unexpected%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20an%20official%20letter%20from%20NID%20equating%20her%20diploma%20to%20a%20post-graduate%20degree%2C%20making%20her%20eligible%20for%20a%20PhD.%20She%20enrolled%20at%20IIT%20Bombay%20and%20completed%20her%20thesis%20over%20eight%20years%2C%20even%20as%20she%20navigated%20personal%20loss%20and%20family%20responsibilities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20husband.%20My%20daughter%20got%20married%20and%20had%20a%20child.%20I%20had%20to%20help%20her.%20But%20I%20kept%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20PhD%20focused%20on%20the%20sustainability%20of%20menstrual%20management%2C%20applying%20what%20she%20calls%20the%20PASS%20model%20%E2%80%94%20Paryavaran%20(Environment)%2C%20Arthik%20(Economics)%2C%20Swasthya%20(Health)%2C%20and%20Samaj%20(Society)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20assess%20menstrual%20products%20holistically.%20%E2%80%9CA%20menstrual%20product%20has%20to%20be%20sustainable%20and%20viable%20from%20these%20four%20angles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20gone%20global.%20Her%20NGO%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%2C%20and%20her%20studio%2C%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20have%20welcomed%20design%20students%20from%20across%20the%20country%20for%20rural%20immersion%20programmes.%20These%20students%20go%20to%20the%20fields%2C%20sketch%2C%20analyse%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20and%20compare%20it%20with%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20Lakshmi%20mentors%20students%20to%20co-create%20health%20visuals%20by%20immersing%20in%20rural%20realities%20and%20community%20dialogue.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FTBI-featured-image-5_11zon-1-1743598682-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417542%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EAt%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20Lakshmi%20mentors%20students%20to%20co-create%20health%20visuals%20by%20immersing%20in%20rural%20realities%20and%20community%20dialogue.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikalpdesign%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20creative%20space%20where%20designers%20and%20artists%20from%20leading%20institutes%20learn%20to%20collaborate%20with%20rural%20communities%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20adolescents%2C%20to%20co-create%20meaningful%20visual%20tools%20around%20reproductive%20health%2C%20nutrition%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20more.%20Her%20visual%20content%20is%20now%20used%20by%20educators%20and%20NGOs%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20world%20finally%20took%20notice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20have%20been%20widely%20recognised%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%98Pride%20of%20NID%E2%80%99%20Award%20(2024)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%98Women%20of%20Substance%20Award%E2%80%99%20by%20Aravali%20Foundation%2C%20Udaipur%20(2022)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccor%20Hospitality%2C%20France%20%E2%80%98Take%20Off%20Challenge%E2%80%99%20Award%20(2021)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGoonj%20Award%3A%20For%20keeping%20Uger%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9CCopy%20Left%E2%80%9D%20Space%20(2019)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPune%20Innovation%20Centre%20(PIC)%20Social%20Innovation%20Recognition%20(2018)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAustralia%20CSC%20Meritorious%20Commendation%20Award%20%E2%80%93%20Centre%20for%20Communication%20and%20Social%20Change%2C%20University%20of%20Queensland%20(2009)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20friend%20and%20colleague%2C%20Smriti%20Kedia%2C%20sums%20it%20up%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CLakshmi%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20been%20path-breaking.%20She%20applied%20design%20to%20communicate%20the%20most%20complex%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20menstrual%20health%2C%20gender%2C%20reproductive%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20to%20non-literate%20communities.%20Her%20contributions%20have%20gone%20beyond%20borders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fhv8EgRUe6qY%3Fsi%3D7uJ_PnoI6zvFCHsQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20design%20approach%20has%20attracted%20designers%20and%20artists%20from%20premium%20institutes%20to%20her%20studio%2C%20Vikalpdesign%2C%20and%20her%20organisation%2C%20Jatan%20Sansthan%2C%20where%20she%20helped%20them%20learn%20and%20collaborate%20with%20rural%20women%2C%20adolescents%2C%20and%20communities%20to%20create%20informed%20and%20meaningful%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smriti%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Lakshmi%20lives%20with%20her%2091-year-old%20mother%2C%20daughter%2C%20and%20grandson.%20She%E2%80%99s%20taken%20up%20ceram